  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study looked at the effect of vitamin D levels on the complications of type 2 diabetes
      and the fat profile of patients with diabetes.Participants in this study were divided into
      two groups. One group included participants with vitamin D deficiency and the other group did
      not.The first group receives 50,000 units of oral vitamin D 3 daily for up to 8 days.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
